    App --> SDK
    SDK --> Program
    Program --> Registry
    Registry --> Program

    Provider --> Risk
    Risk --> Attestation
    Attestation --> Registry

    Program -->|Allow / Reject| App

### Why this slaps
- Auditors instantly understand scope
- Devs instantly understand flow
- Investors instantly understand moat

